{"tid":2097372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【集思廣益】買書送俾在囚手足有冇得諗？","createTime":"2020-07-06T18:31:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T02:32:55.000Z","uid":47593,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"61efb196df8799e26eca1c63d3d7e4acca38687a","tid":2097372,"uid":47593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T18:31:33.000Z","msg":"喺入面可以做嘅嘢有限，日子一定好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我記得陳健民教授話佢坐監睇咗好多書，咁即係外面嘅人可以送書入去？<br />\n有書睇下過下日晨，甚至乎增進下知識，日子應該可以好過啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇可能搵邵家臻或者其他議員幫幫手，我哋買啲書搵佢哋送入去？"},{"pid":"4cab7a4bf50437fc84c2bd493c7b9b8af030c415","tid":2097372,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T18:54:35.000Z","msg":"唔係應該問咗手足想睇咩書先？"},{"pid":"c953451386b88bfbf0df81012f821a975a72c78b","tid":2097372,"uid":47593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cab7a4bf50437fc84c2bd493c7b9b8af030c415","tid":2097372,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T18:54:35.000Z","msg":"唔係應該問咗手足想睇咩書先？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T19:09:49.000Z","msg":"如果計劃可行，有議員幫手，到時先收集意見？"},{"pid":"f024daa0d370383d47604b8ff62882504c9bc834","tid":2097372,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c953451386b88bfbf0df81012f821a975a72c78b","tid":2097372,"uid":47593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cab7a4bf50437fc84c2bd493c7b9b8af030c415","tid":2097372,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T18:54:35.000Z","msg":"唔係應該問咗手足想睇咩書先？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T19:09:49.000Z","msg":"如果計劃可行，有議員幫手，到時先收集意見？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T19:18:01.000Z","msg":"熱狗黃兆健有收集"},{"pid":"c3eafbba87a5df4ef2e5150dcdc00d1f6a1f6604","tid":2097372,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T19:18:36.000Z","msg":"好似一個月可以入四本<br />\n所以陳健民一星期睇完一本"},{"pid":"1f185809cc4e4b4b22471678a6d67813c0570